ed="T" n="0847a02"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0847a02"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000005324"><placeName>代州</placeName><placeName>北臺山</placeName></placeName><persName key="A009478">隱峯</persName>傳（<persName key="A012836">亡名</persName> <persName key="A012837">雉鳩和尚</persName><ptr target="#n635"/>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0847a03"/><persName key="A009478">釋隱峯</persName>，俗姓<name>鄧</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000018253"><placeName>建州</placeName><placeName>邵武</placeName></placeName>人也。稚歲憨狂，<lb
ed="T" n="0847a04"/>不侚父母之命<ptr target="#n2734"/>，出家納法<ptr target="#n2736"/>。後往觀方，見<placeName key="PL000000016923">池<lb
ed="T" n="0847a05"/>陽</placeName><persName key="A003889">南泉<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，令取澡罐，提舉相應，為<persName key="A003889">願<roleName>公</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0847a06"/>所許焉<ptr target="#n2737"/>，終認嗣<persName key="A003623">馬<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>耳<ptr target="#n2735"/>。<persName key="A009478">峯</persName><date notBefore-iso="+0806-01-29" key="j20154742020606" notAfter-iso="+0820-02-17"><name>元和</name>中</date><ptr target="#n2739"/>言遊<lb
ed="T" n="0847a07"/><placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺山</placeName>，路出<placeName key="PL000000023026">淮西</placeName>，屬<persName key="A010372">吳元濟</persName>阻兵<ptr target="#n2738"/>，違拒王<lb
ed="T" n="0847a08"/>命。官軍與賊遇，交鋒未決勝負。<persName key="A009478">峯</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A009478">我</ref>去<lb
ed="T" n="0847a09"/>解其殺戮。」乃擲錫空中，飛身冉冉隨去，介<lb
ed="T" n="0847a10"/>兩軍陣過，戰士各觀僧飛騰，不覺抽戈匣<lb
ed="T" n="0847a11"/>刃焉。既而遊遍靈跡，忽於<placeName key="PL000000005328">金剛窟</placeName>前倒立<lb
ed="T" n="0847a12"/>而死，亭亭然其直如植<ptr target="#n2740"/>。時議靈穴之前，當<lb
ed="T" n="0847a13"/>舁就爇<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1795"/>，屹定如山，併力不動，遠近瞻覩，驚<lb
ed="T" n="0847a14"/>歎希奇。<persName key="A009478">峯</persName>有妹為尼，入<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺</placeName>，瞋目咄之<lb
ed="T" n="0847a15"/>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A009478">老兄</ref>疇昔為不循法律，死且熒惑於人。」<lb
ed="T" n="0847a16"/>時眾已知妹雖骨肉，豈敢携貳<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1796"/>，請從恒度<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1797"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0847a17"/>以手輕攘，僨然<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1798"/>而仆。遂<anchor xml:id="beg0847sgsz1"/>荼毘<anchor xml:id="end0847sgsz1"/>之，收舍利入<lb
ed="T" n="0847a18"/>塔<ptr target="#n2741"/>，號<persName key="A009478">鄧隱峯</persName>。遺一頌云：「獨絃琴子為君<lb
ed="T" n="0847a19"/>彈，松柏長青不怯寒，金鑛相和性自別，任<lb
ed="T" n="0847a20"/>向君前試取看。」</p><p xml:id="pT50p0847a2101"><lb
ed="T" n="0847a21"/>系曰：僵屍累足，於事一同；立逝坐亡，為修<lb
ed="T" n="0847a22"/>三昧<ptr target="#n2742"/>。此者頭搘<ptr type="glossary" target="#g125"/>厚載<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1799"/>，履蹈青冥<ptr type="glossary" target="#g820"/>，逆恒理以<lb
ed="T" n="0847a23"/>難知，諒是人而不測。若斯倒置，振古一人。<lb
ed="T" n="0847a24"/>其妹尼之<anchor xml:id="beg0847001"/>攘<anchor xml:id="end0847001"/>也，若<persName key="A006021">屈平</persName>為<persName key="A023841">女𡡓</persName>之罵焉。如<lb
ed="T" n="0847a25"/>幻之功，善權<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1124"/>大矣。或曰：「<placeName key="PL000000023026">淮西</placeName>之役，《唐書》胡弗<lb
ed="T" n="0847a26"/>載<persName key="A009478">隱峯</persName>飛錫解陣邪？」通曰：「小說所傳，或得<lb
ed="T" n="0847a27"/>其實。是故《春秋》一經，五家作傳，可得同乎？」</p><p xml:id="pT50p0847a2801"><lb
ed="T" n="0847a28"/>又<placeName key="PL000000035305"><placeName>漢州</placeName><placeName>開化寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A012836">釋亡名</persName>，先因入寺，見瑞應交<lb
ed="T" n="0847a29"/>現，遂誓捨身，剋苦為期。忽於殿中焚香<pb ed="T" n="0847b" xml:id="T50.2061.0847b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0847b01"/>次，俄覩地屋皆為瑠璃色，有菩薩乘五色<lb
ed="T" n="0847b02"/>雲下庭中曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A012836">汝</ref>極堅至，必當得道，吾<anchor xml:id="beg0847sgsz3"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>求</sic><corr>來</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0847sgsz3"/>證<lb
ed="T" n="0847b03"/><ref type="person" target="#A012836">汝</ref>。」<persName key="A012836">亡名</persName>叩頭<anchor xml:id="beg0847sgsz5"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0847sgsz5"/>拜，斯須不見。寺僧至云「學<lb
ed="T" n="0847b04"/>院內皆變瑠璃色。」<anchor xml:id="beg0847sgsz7"/>歎<anchor xml:id="end0847sgsz7"/>嗟不已。其僧復勤節<lb
ed="T" n="0847b05"/>行焉。</p><p xml:id="pT50p0847b0601"><lb
ed="T" n="0847b06"/>又<placeName key="PL000000025497">鄧州</placeName>有僧<persName key="A012837">亡名</persName>，年且衰朽，遊行<placeName key="PL000000027118"><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>穰</sic><corr>襄</corr></choice></placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000025497">鄧</placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0847002"/>州<anchor xml:id="end0847002"/><lb
ed="T" n="0847b07"/>間<ptr target="#n2743"/>，日食二雉鳩，僧俗共非之。<ref type="person" target="#A012837">老僧</ref>終無避<lb
ed="T" n="0847b08"/>迴。嘗饌羞之次，有貧士求飡，分其二足與<lb
ed="T" n="0847b09"/>之食。食訖，<ref type="person" target="#A012837">老僧</ref>盥漱，雙鳩從口而出，一則能<lb
ed="T" n="0847b10"/>行，一則匍匐在地。貧士驚怪，亦吐其飯，其鳩<lb
ed="T" n="0847b11"/>二足復全。<ref type="person" target="#A012837">其僧</ref>實不食此禽<ptr target="#n2744"/>。自爾眾人崇<lb
ed="T" n="0847b12"/>重，號曰<placeName key="PL000000025497">南陽</placeName><persName key="A012837">鴙鳩和尚</persName>也。有<anchor xml:id="beg0847sgsz9"/>歎<anchor xml:id="end0847sgsz9"/>之曰：「昔<placeName key="PL000000034982">青<lb
ed="T" n="0847b13"/>城山</placeName><persName key="A006906">香<anchor xml:id="beg0847sgsz11"/>闍黎<anchor xml:id="end0847sgsz11"/></persName>飲酒啖肴，然後吐出，鷄羊肉<lb
ed="T" n="0847b14"/>皆化作本形，飛鳴而入坑穴中，同也<ptr target="#n2745"/>。」</p>
